<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>- وَكَثْرَةُ دُعَاءٍ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>- وَصَلَاةٍ عَلَى النَّبِيِّ صَلَّى اللهُ عَلَيْهِ وَسَلَّمَ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>- وَمَنْ دَخَلَ وَالإِمَامُ يَخْطُبُ؛ لَمْ يَجْلِسْ حَتَّى يَرْكَعَ رَكْعَتَيْنِ خَفِيفَتَيْنِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>فَصْلٌ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>- وَصَلَاةُ العِيدَيْنِ فَرْضُ كِفَايةٍ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> وَوَقْتُهَا:</span> كَصَلَاةِ الضُّحَى.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> وَشُرُوطُهَا:</span> كَالجُمُعَةِ، مَا عَدَا الخُطْبَتَيْنِ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> فَإِنْ لَمْ يُعْلَمْ بِالعِيدِ إِلَّا بَعْدَ الزَّوَالِ:</span> صَلَّوْا مِنَ الغَدِ قَضَاءً.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> وَتُسَنَّ:</span><a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>- بِصَحْرَاءَ قَرِيبَةٍ عُرْفًا.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>- وَسُنَّ تَبْكِيرُ مَأْمُومٍ بَعْدَ صَلَاةِ الصُّبْحِ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>- عَلَى أَحْسَنِ هَيْئَةٍ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>- مَاشِيًا.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>- وَتَأَخُّرُ إِمَامٍ إِلَى وَقْتِ الصَّلَاةِ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>- وَالتَّوسِعَةُ عَلَى الأَهْلِ.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>